[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "はぁ、はぁっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00543",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "手間かけさせるね。ここまでだよ、シトリン。\n神妙にしな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00544",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いつものあんたならもっと苦戦してた。\nでも、今のあんたは破れかぶれになってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00545",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "こんなの後悔することになると思うけどね。\n僕のやり方が一番丸い、一番正しいってさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00546",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "正しいかどうかはともかくとして、\n私はクリセルダたちを「管理」なんてしたくない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00547",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それにヘルトたちも止めてみせる。\nだから安心して！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00548",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "安心できるか！　あの二人について\n記憶を失ってるの、羨ましいぐらいだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00549",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私、昔はあの二人にビビッてたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00550",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ビビッていたというか、制圧されてたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00551",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "あの二人がヤバいってのは同感さ。\n腕っぷしで言えば九偉人の中でも別格だからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00552",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "でも、限りなく薄い勝算だろうが、\n戦わなきゃいけないときがあるのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00553",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "大人しく従っておけば僕らの命は無事なのに、\nなんで、わざわざここで意地を張るのかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00554",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "イェルカはなんか覚悟決めちゃってるけど、\n私は別に死ぬ気ないわよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00555",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "どれだけ強かろうが、あの性格よ。アウグストたちの\n命令にだって素直に従ってるわけじゃないんでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00556",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "実はちょっと考えていることがあるの。\nそれにはイェルカとシトリンの力が必要なんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00557",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "考えてること？\nなんだい、そりゃあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00558",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "突破口ってやつよ。力ずくで止めてみせたわけだし、\nシトリンも協力してくれるわよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00559",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "このやり方は話し合いに近いけど、ちょっと違うの。\n怒らせる可能性もあるかもだけど、いける気がするのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00560",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]